@endnode

@node Bugs "Bugs"
BUGS

As far as i know, UniDial has no bugs. However, there is ONE thing that
might cause some trouble with other programs using audio:  The audio
routines were written in assembler, using pretty low-level access to the
audio-hardware.

I hope this won't turn out to be a real problem (in that case i promise to
fix it).

@endnode


